 H         6.798969        6.113001        8.252001
 H         7.499969        4.660001        7.500000
    &END COORD
    &KIND H
      BASIS_SET DZVP-GTH
      POTENTIAL GTH-PBE
    &END KIND 
    &KIND C
      BASIS_SET DZVP-GTH
      POTENTIAL GTH-PBE
    &END KIND 
  &END SUBSYS
&END FORCE_EVAL

